Configuration.Name: TI AM263x/AM243x/AM64x Sample
Configuration.Info: Shall be set if the Slave code executes on an AM263x/AM243x/AM64x device (CPU: ARM Cortex-R5F) . The application should run on an AM263x/AM243x/AM64x EVM Board from Texas Instruments and requires the MCU_PLUS_SDK for building the project.
